Attention... three-four!

2
00:00:38,378 --> 00:00:40,014
<i>One silent...</i>

3
00:00:40,895 --> 00:00:44,043
<i>divine night of May</i>

4
00:00:45,011 --> 00:00:47,966
<i>you said that you would stay</i>

5
00:00:48,767 --> 00:00:51,483
<i>after our first date.</i>

6
00:00:54,601 --> 00:00:56,271
<i>It's night now</i>

7
00:00:57,238 --> 00:01:00,193
<i>deep darkness makes me sad</i>

8
00:01:01,273 --> 00:01:04,342
<i>all alone in her bed</i>

9
00:01:04,989 --> 00:01:08,296
<i>Marijana is so late.</i>

10
00:01:10,264 --> 00:01:11,900
<i>And I'm</i>

11
00:01:12,381 --> 00:01:16,053
<i>alone under a palm</i>

12
00:01:16,537 --> 00:01:20,003
<i>sleep is closing up my eyes</i>

13
00:01:20,653 --> 00:01:22,766
<i>all sad, I'm longing</i>

14
00:01:23,170 --> 00:01:25,362
<i>for the day to come.</i>

15
00:01:25,767 --> 00:01:28,437
<i>Oh, Marijana</i>

16
00:01:29,803 --> 00:01:33,428
<i>sweet little Marijana</i>

17
00:01:33,878 --> 00:01:37,072
<i>I will be waiting here
till the daylight comes!</i>

18
00:01:37,593 --> 00:01:42,153
IRONING MAN'S SHIRTS HERE

19
00:01:58,572 --> 00:02:01,447
<i>Oh, Marijana</i>

20
00:02:02,328 --> 00:02:05,873
<i>sweet Iittle Marijana</i>

21
00:02:06,483 --> 00:02:10,108
<i>I will be waiting here</i>

22
00:02:10,519 --> 00:02:14,190
<i>'cause you will come!</i>

23
00:02:26,262 --> 00:02:31,853
ONE SONG A DAY
KEEPS MISCHIEF AWAY

24
